## pyproject.toml essentials

```toml
[project]
requires-python = ">=3.9"

[tool.pytest.ini_options]
testpaths = ["tests"]
addopts = ["--strict-markers", "--cov=myproject"]

[tool.mypy]
strict = true
disallow_untyped_defs = true
```
